msgid "‘samaṇadūsīvāyaṃ samaṇapalāpo samaṇakāraṇḍavo’ti."
msgstr "a corrupt ascetic, just useless trash."

msgctxt "an8.10:4.5"
msgid "Tamenaṃ iti viditvā bahiddhā nāsenti."
msgstr "When they realize this they send him away."

msgctxt "an8.10:4.6"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "an8.10:4.7"
